OL,4,Ccompany over 'serious issues'
OL,6,FHolidaymakers are being urged to avoid
OL,7,Fa car hire company ranked last in a
OL,8,Fcustomer satisfaction survey.
OL,10,FGoldcar, which operates in countries
OL,11,Fsuch as Spain, Portugal, France and
OL,12,Fthe US, achieved an overall score of
OL,13,F52% in the annual report by consumer
OL,14,Fgroup Which?
OL,16,FIt was awarded just two stars out of a
OL,17,Fpossible five for value for money, car
OL,18,Fdescription matching reality, record
OL,19,Fgiven of damage to car, and customer
OL,20,Fservice.
