OL,3,CTourists urged to avoid car hire
OL,4,Ccompany over 'serious issues'
OL,6,FOne fifth (20%) of respondents who
OL,7,Fused Goldcar said they had issues with
OL,8,Fthe condition of the car, and 23%
OL,9,Freported being charged extra either
OL,10,Fwhen they picked up or returned the
OL,11,Fcar.
OL,13,FWhich? said its previous
OL,14,Finvestigations found cases of the
OL,15,Fbusiness engaging in "pressure selling
OL,16,Ftactics" to encourage customers to buy
OL,17,Fextra insurance at the desk.
